# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Ezydrag AI SEO Suite — Environment Variables
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your credentials.
# Only GOOGLE_API_KEY is REQUIRED. Others are optional
# but enable richer data collection.

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
# 1. GOOGLE API KEY (REQUIRED)
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Used for: Gemini LLM + PageSpeed Insights API
# Get one free at: https://aistudio.google.com/apikey
GOOGLE_API_KEY=your-gemini-api-key-here

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
# 2. GOOGLE SEARCH CONSOLE (OPTIONAL)
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Used for: Keyword rankings, CTR, traffic data
# Setup steps:
#   1. Create a Google Cloud project at https://console.cloud.google.com
#   2. Enable "Google Search Console API"
#   3. Create a Service Account and download the JSON key file
#   4. Add the service account email as a user in Search Console
#   5. Set the path to the JSON file below
GSC_CREDENTIALS_PATH=path/to/your-service-account.json

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
# 3. BACKLINK PROVIDER (OPTIONAL — pick ONE)
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
# The system auto-detects which provider you've configured.
# Priority order: DataForSEO → Semrush → Ahrefs
# Only configure ONE of these three options.

# ── Option A: DataForSEO (RECOMMENDED — cheapest) ──
# Cost: Pay-as-you-go (~$0.002 per API task)
# Sign up: https://app.dataforseo.com/register
# You get $1.00 free credit on signup
DATAFORSEO_LOGIN=your-email@example.com
DATAFORSEO_PASSWORD=your-dataforseo-password

# ── Option B: Semrush ──
# Cost: Requires Business plan ($499.95/month) + API units
# API key: Found in Semrush → Account → Subscription Info → API Units
# SEMRUSH_API_KEY=your-semrush-api-key

# ── Option C: Ahrefs ──
# Cost: Requires Enterprise plan ($1,499/month) + API units
# API key: Found in Ahrefs → Account Settings → API Keys
# AHREFS_API_KEY=your-ahrefs-api-key
